Sunday, June 15 to Saturday, June 21.

Camp Alta - 794 Alta Power House Rd, Alta, CA 95701

The camper application for Eastwood Leadership Camp 2025 is now open! Eastwood Leadership Camp is open to campers entering 5th-9th grade. This year's camp will take place at a new location, from June 15-21 (see below for details). The application will remain open until May 15, 2025.


An email with details about the counselor/ranger application has been sent separately. Applicants will be accepted based on merit, participation in activities of Garber House and Menlough Study Center throughout the year, and on their application itself.

Dates and location:
Eastwood Leadership Camp will take place from Sunday, June 15th at 3 PM to Saturday, June 21st, 2025 at 1 PM.

Camp will take place at Camp Alta located at 794 Alta Power House Rd, Alta, CA 95701

Application and Payment
To apply for camp please go to eastwoodleadershipcamp.org, fill out the application form, and submit the payment. Checks can also be sent to Eastwood Study Center, Inc. at 1827 Oxford St, Apt 1, Berkeley, CA 94709.

If you would like to pay in installments - for example, weekly installments - you can use the "$100 Payment" option. Please keep track of the installments you have made.

An early bird rate discount of $50 per camper will be available until March 31, 2025. (After March 31, the regular cost for a camper is $700. Please see the site for more details on cost.)
Financial support is available.
